prompt_text: Describe the scene of a school playground.
content_text: The kids were. Outside playing on the playground. When one of them fell from the swing. All the other children ran to his aid. Then the teacher went outside and yelled what is happening. Old children let the teacher know what happened. So the teacher helped the kid that fell to the ground by applying some ointment on his knee. Then they went inside the classroom because the. Class was starting. And that's it.
